1\"/> || Kyle's mother, who is overbearing and usually overreacts to anything slightly offensive.\n| \"[[Death (South Park)|Death]]\"<ref name=official2009/>\n|-\n| {{sort|Broflovski, Ike|[[Ike Broflovski]]}}\n| various children of ''South Park'' employees<ref name=\"faq-23apr2002\" /> || Kyle's younger brother, the Canadian-born adopted son of Gerald and Sheila\n| \"[[Cartman Gets an Anal Probe]]\"<ref name=official2009/>\n|-\n| {{sort|Cartman, Liane|[[Liane Cartman]]}}\n| Mary Kay Bergman, Eliza Schneider, April Stewart<ref name=\"autogenerated1\"/> ||Cartman's overly indulgent mother, who spoils her son.<ref name=\"faq-19apr2001\">{{cite web|url=http://www.southparkstudios.com/fans/faq/archives.php?month=4&year=2001 |title=FAQ: April 2001 |accessdate=2008-10-13 |date=2001-04-19 |publisher=southparkstudios.com |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090328120915/http://www.southparkstudios.com/fans/faq/archives.php?month=4&year=2001 |archivedate=2009-03-28 }}</ref>\n| \"[[Cartman Gets an Anal Probe]]\"<ref name=official2009/>\n|-\n| {{sort|McCormick, Stuart|[[Stuart McCormick]]}}\n| Matt Stone<ref name=\"faq-23apr2002\" /> || Kenny's alcoholic and violent father\n| \"[[Death (South Park)|Death]]\"<ref name=official2009/>\n|-\n| {{sort|McCormick, Carol|[[Stuart and Carol McCormick|Carol McCormick]]}}\n| Mary Kay Bergman, Eliza Schneider,<ref name=\"autogenerated1\"/> [[April Stewart]]<ref name=\"premiere1\"/> || Kenny's alcoholic and violent mother\n| \"[[Starvin' Marvin (South Park)|Starvin' Marvin]]\"<ref name=official2009/>\n|-\n| {{sort|McCormick, Karen|[[Karen McCormick]]}}\n| Celeste Javier, [[Colleen Villard]]<ref name=\"faq-23apr2002\" />\n|| Kenny's shy and reclusive younger sister, who looks to Kenny for protection and comfort when she is upset\n| \"[[Best Friends Forever (South Park)|Best Friends Forever]]\"<ref name=official2009/>\n|-\n| {{sort|McCormick, Kevin|[[Kevin McCormick (South Park)|Kevin McCormick]]}}\n|  Trey Parker<ref nam